snippet.textDisplay: Whenever I miss someone who is beyond reach, beyond this world, there is no place I could only think of - to go to except listening to Asma Ul-husna. Indeed, hearing all of His 99 names, I feel and I know that I'm just a tiny dust in this endless universe and I know only Allah can connect me to my late mom. Only Allah can convey my sorrow...and only Allah can heal me and show me the path to keep on moving, standing on my own feet..I am so blessed to be born as a muslim, in a muslim family. Alhamdulillah for this pain, alhamdulillah for this loneliness, alhamdulillah for always bringing me home ❤
